{"lastModified":1769607145490,"uri":"c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nWith a sturdy structure crafted from the finest mahogany, Anđeo combines a beautiful classic exterior with a surprisingly modern and luxurious interior.\n\nThe saloon is an exquisite combination of modern and traditional, with highly polished dark and light wood creating a calm, restful ambiance. This is a great place to watch your chef prepare your dinner in the open plan galley, viewed from the comfortable dining corner with a large couch and dining table.\n\nThe contemporary, clean lines of the interior extend to the vast foredeck with ample sunbeds for every guest, while the shaded aft deck provides a spacious, calm oasis, for alfresco dining.","blueprint":{"name":"ANDEO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d73d00e0-f438-11ef-870f-a3ca3892ed79/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fb865420-777c-11f0-a7dc-45b684f9e8e3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::131843a0-777d-11f0-a152-d9c58f418839/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::16907a70-777d-11f0-a152-d9c58f418839/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1a61a6b0-777d-11f0-a152-d9c58f418839/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1d5bd3e0-777d-11f0-a152-d9c58f418839/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::20765a50-777d-11f0-a152-d9c58f418839/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cc4fad-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2492c060-777d-11f0-a152-d9c58f418839/{imageVar